bout profits necessarily; our opposition to labeling of GMOs is common sense really. I\r\nmean, haven\'t you ever been so proud of something you created that you would go to absolutely any\r\nlengths to conceal it?\r\nSK: umm...\r\nHG: That\'s why I\'m using all the financial and political resources of the greatest biotechnology\r\ncompany on Earth to fight the misinformation & to change the minds of the misguided people who\r\njudge our products with skepticism just because we poisoned a few million people in the past.\r\nSK: Wait, what?\r\nHG: GMOs are safe to eat. In fact, our products are so safe & so healthy for people and the\r\nenvironment that I will label them over my dead body.\r\n\r\n<blockquote\r\n</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://ec2-54-68-184-179.us-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Monsanto CEO: GMOs will be labeled over my dead body','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2015-10-18 03:31:47','2015-10-18 03:31:47','',2,'http://ec2-54-68-184-179.us-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com/index.php/2015/10/18/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(9,1,'2015-10-18 03:34:51','2015-10-18 03:34:51','ST. LOUIS – Polls show that over 90% of US consumers think that foods containing genetically\r\nmodified organisms (GMOs) should be labeled as such. Monsanto is one of the largest producers of\r\nGM seeds, in a recent interview their CEO, Hugh Grant, explains why his company is doing\r\neverything in its power to fight mandatory GMO labeling laws.\r\n\r\n<strong>SK:</strong> So, what are some of the issues associated with labeling GM fo