esticide usage, so why are you trying to buy\r\nSyngenta, the largest pesticide producer in the world?\r\n\r\n<strong>HG:</strong> Just in case\r\n\r\n<strong>SK:</strong> What about cross-pollination? How can an organic farmer protect his crops from contamination\r\nfrom a neighboring GM field?\r\n\r\n<strong>HG:</strong> GMOs are safe to eat\r\n\r\n<strong>SK:</strong> Many GMO farmers grow just a few types of plants. Doesn\'t this “mono-cropping” make our food system vulnerable?\r\n\r\n<strong>HG:</strong> Right, but the thing is GMOs are safe to eat.\r\n\r\n<strong>SK:</strong> Do you think if GM foods were labeled in the US your company would lose money?\r\n\r\n<strong>HG:</strong> It\'s not about profits necessarily; our opposition to labeling of GMOs is common sense really. I\r\nmean, haven\'t you ever been so proud of something you created that you would go to absolutely any\r\nlengths to conceal it?\r\n\r\n<strong>SK:</strong> umm...\r\n\r\n<strong>HG:</strong> That\'s why I\'m using all the financial and political resources of the greatest biotechnology\r\ncompany on Earth to fight the misinformation & to change the minds of the misguided people who\r\njudge our products with skepticism just because we poisoned a few million people in the past.\r\n\r\n<strong>SK:</strong> Wait, what?\r\n\r\n<strong>HG:</strong> Our products are so safe & so healthy for people and the\r\nenvironment that I will label them over my dead body.\r\n','Monsanto CEO: \'GMOs will be labeled over my dead body\'','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2015-10-21 16:58:37','2015-10-21 16:58:37','',2,'http://ec2-54-68-184-179.us-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com/index.php/2015/10/21/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(32,1,'2015-10-21 17:00:04','2015-10-21 17:00:04','<font size=\"8\">Monsanto CEO: \'GMOs will be labeled over my dead body\'</font>\r\n\r\nby <a href=\"https://twitter.com/skennycomedy\">Sarah Kenny</a>\r\n\r\nST. LOUIS – Polls show that over 90% of US consume