11-02 02:58:46','2015-11-02 02:58:46','blah blah','WHO Report Flawed: Bacon & Hot Dogs Actually Cure Cancer','','inherit','closed','closed','','50-revision-v1','','','2015-11-02 02:58:46','2015-11-02 02:58:46','',50,'http://ec2-54-68-184-179.us-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com/index.php/2015/11/02/50-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(60,1,'2015-11-02 03:00:12','2015-11-02 03:00:12','yo yo ma','How does this look?','','trash','open','open','','how-does-this-look','','','2015-11-02 04:03:49','2015-11-02 04:03:49','',0,'http://ec2-54-68-184-179.us-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com/?p=60',0,'post','',0),(61,1,'2015-11-02 03:00:12','2015-11-02 03:00:12','yo yo ma','How does this look?','','inherit','closed','closed','','60-revision-v1','','','2015-11-02 03:00:12','2015-11-02 03:00:12','',60,'http://ec2-54-68-184-179.us-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com/index.php/2015/11/02/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(62,1,'2015-11-02 03:20:56','2015-11-02 03:20:56','<font size=\"8\">Monsanto CEO: \'GMOs will be labeled over my dead body\'</font>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_37\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"857\"]<a href=\"http://ec2-54-68-184-179.us-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/photo4.jpg\"><img src=\"http://ec2-54-68-184-179.us-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/photo4.jpg\" alt=\"some corn somewhere \" width=\"857\" height=\"515\" class=\"size-full wp-image-37\" /></a> some corn somewhere [/caption]\r\nby <a href=\"http://skennycomedy.com/\">Sarah Kenny</a> October 21, 2015\r\n\r\nST. LOUIS – Polls show that over 90% of US consumers think that foods containing genetically\r\nmodified organisms (GMOs) should be labeled as such. Monsanto is one of the largest producers of\r\nGM seeds, in a recent interview their CEO, Hugh Grant, explains why his company is doing\r\neverything in its power to fight mandatory GMO labeling laws.\r\n\r\n<strong>SK:</strong> So, what are some of the issues associated with labeling GM foods?\r\n\r\n<strong>HG:</strong>